xaaramiyahow xaarka wayn hanala qabsan qaniis labeeya tahe buris in madaca lagaaga tuma mudan tahay , wacela iska dhalen saasa wacel ku noqote balayo ilka bolala lahe qaniis yahow qaniska dhale , xaar wenka tahay cun nacala aabaha iyo meel lga keene ku yaale damiir lawayhow walashiis lagu ag kufsade

qaniis hadu jiro adaa aabe u ah nacala la naaso wayned sidi dumarke wax ku sheganayo maleh , wecelada waligoode ia aruursan jiren adna waka mid tahay eey yahow eeygu dhale , nacalada adee kugu soo dagte see kaga muqata ka dareeme

naago adi camal dhilo wacelada an utirsanen xafadahae wasaqeesa noga guur xaafada gabdha sharaf lahaa no jooge , naag walbo soo walataa anaga hanagu soo hoos dhuumato qumay walbana anaga hanagu soo riixo waxu arkaa , qooq baa ku haayo wilyahow dayuuska balse soomali horee utiri qooq ma jabe ninkisa jabo

qaniis aan adi aheen hore uma jirin hoyada wase dadki adaa haleeye walaguugu qasaare nacas yahow nasaha wayn  , balaayo madax yariis ah leh yaa ushegysa ina wacel laso helay tahay darbi jiif yasha kamid aheed , dofarti ku dhashay was nacala aabaha ku yaalo

eey eey dhale ana ila hadle miyaa adoo caloshan dhulka xaaqeso leh dayuus an damiir laheena tahay nacalaa kugu taale , qof yahow madaxa gariga leh wajigan folxumada badan iga kor leexi balaayo foolxuma badane  , wacel wacel kala jirina tahay nacala dayuuska tahay ku yaal anaga talefanada nagu dhagesane

doofarti ku dhashay was nacala firkaaga iyo faracaaga ku yaal eey yahow eygu dhale , nacalaa madaxada koombada leh ku taalo wacel yahow qaabta daran afka doqoshka leh hanala hadlin , hanala tirsan qooq baa meela is gayso waysee qaniis yahow wax mataraha ahnaaag ku rabtaa wayse , nin gaabana nin ah ya ku yirir awalba nacala wajigaga xunka ku yaale

shaqbooyinka nocaga kale waku jirkoda iibsan jore yaa igu qaldesa naya danbe lambarkeyga haku so qaldomin , nin soo waashe uma horeysid ee madaxa darbiyada ka ilaalso lee qof ku rabto malahe , sharaf inadan laheen hadaa qof aduunka di kaso harto kuma qaaten qof ku rabtana ma jisrto dayuus yahow nasaha dheer

dharka inaa nala xirato lee kaa soo dhaw qaniis yahow qiyaanada badan nacalaa kugu taale wacel wacel kala jirina tahay balaayo foolxuma badane qaniis ahee , nimanka iyo naagaha hotelada habenki waqti danbe joogo waxba isma dhaaman qurunla yaasha , zino doon hada maqashid wa adinka habenadi hotelada waregaya nacala idinku taale

sharmuutada tahay was eey yahey eeydu dhashe , kii ku dhalaa kugu qasaare balaayo daba wayn dhila ah saas habeen iyo maalin kii ku dhale oga cabaaji , dhiikarka cidada adaa ku ride sharaf laay yahey doqonya ah ilkaha dhaadher

ilka dhaadheerta tahay was nacala firkaga iyo mesha kaso baxdeba ku taalebalayo af turumbo leh lugahan qaroofan meaha kask wado naag walana tahee , nacala washisiyadaada ku taalo calool wayn yahow caloosha qashinka leh waxu galo iyo waxu guda aysan jirin , sixiloore waynaada tahay quraafi ah ma saana rabtay ina dad ku daweso

doqon doqon dhale nacala aabaha ku yaal ciyaal cana boorahan yaa mesha nookenay nacala firkiisa ahee , nacas foolxuma badana tahay balaayo af qalocan ilka doqosha leh , eey damiirka laga qaada tahay naag naag yahey jileeca badan is walaaqan iga dhaaf wax ma tara yahow

wax lagu qasaara tagay shalayto uma dhimana hooyadi ku dhashay iyo aabihi ku sugay intaso sano , shiirayaha tahay cun shirkaga dadba ku dhiman gaaray boosaneer ka darana noqote , waxan waligiis biyo isku taabana tahay qurunlaha tahay cun balaayo shiir badan

dayuusyada noocago kale hadal kuma darsano nacas yahow nasaha wayn , jiis yahow jiiska dhalome lugaha qalocan hadal soo baro nacalaa ku dhalee , sharaf malihid xaywan yahow qanjaha wayn balaayo san doofar kuu lahaate

af garaashka tahay was nacala firkaga iyo faracaga ku yaal eey eey dhale afku qurun badnede , wad dhaqan xuntahay danbe afka ila soo gal qayanoole yahow qaabta daran qumayga ah , lo'da tahay was eey yahow eeygu dhale nooga bax meesha washinsiyadaada cunee
garguurte dulaysanaa tahay madaxa gaalada hoos dhigo nacala ku dhale , afkan baqaarka ad moodo naga qari nacala ku dhale , badaa gadataa wali kugu haysanaa bee goorme is sharxayse adna tuug yahow

hadal af macaani tuugnima ahaa wadaa daacad kaam ahan waxan , dayac iyo dayuusnimaa udhaxaysaa waligaba kama baxdid intas , waxa sheegataba wa ku shalayto qayr kuma hadashid ileene , xafadaha tuug utagana tahay maskin iska dhigaya

nin siyaayasi alle ka cabsanaayo inu jiro ilama ahan nin walba caloshiisu xilka uradsadaa , waxaad na taraysid naftada tar ayada kaga baahane  , tiisa daryeela tukale ku dara la dhahay waxa is tarto allah ku tuso anaga waxba kama rabnee

xilka iyo xaaranta wa walaalo hada xil qabata xaran waku jirta kama baxsano , munaafiq an fakir lahena tahay hadalkaga iska hor imaanayo waxa ku hadleaid kow soo xafid sidi wax walan ha is tooganine , waxan kugu nacay hadal badnida iyo wax tar la'anta

waligaa saan kama baxaysid hadaa munaqnimo ku jirtid tuug meel laso istaajiya noqote nacas yahow  , caacle ado ahaa rabta ina xil utartanto yaka caqli badan tahay dabaal yahow aqonta lahen jaahilka ah , nin dayacan dantiis ma gartaa markan maamul nalogu dhigay maxu so kordhin karaa

macalin an waxba aqoone madada nogu dhiiben wu iska xoogsana asna , wax walba aragno run mahan dayuus walba suud noso xiranayo waxu iskaga ka dhiga nin fican aqyaar ah , baadiya ku sugan tahay markam waxan laguu dirsana faraha la gashe

nin dhano sano so tartamaaye cod helaa tahay , waxa tarto dadka waxa burburisa ka badan afsoomaligan kama dhagysaneno ha is daalin xilkan ku dhaaf , shacab hadu wax dooran lahaa dayuus adi camal maso baxeen qiyaanole kaas camalna ma doorten doqon kan camalna ma qaaten ki udaneye doran lahayen

waxa sheegto iyo ficilkaga kala duwan nin walbo siyaasina wa sidaas , waxa balan qaadaysan o dhan wa waxa nagu so xira galinaysan dhab idinkama ahan carurtina iyo qarabadina basa wax tartan , dhiiqoyinkasa ku nooshahay ana rabtaa ina ila tartanto soo waynow warkaga ana arkayo run iyo beene

dalka waxu la burbure wa dad adinko kale ine u tartamayan , hormarka waxaa noo diide doqon adi camal ina mar doorano farta noogu dhacde , nin walba intusan iman buu afka buura ka dhisaa marku xilka qabtana mudul ma dhiso sidi nin wax haayo sawiro so galaa bas

inadan i hor imaan waku mahdiya wajigaga xumihis ina ku xanunsadaa laga yaabi lahaa hadi kale , waxaa gasho iyo waxa gudaba ma arkin mar walba abaal ina gashaa shegta  , nin abaal sheegte nin maahan mid sadaqana uma ahan istustusu ku dhiibe

hadaa sacadan wax qabsan laheed heera gaari lahed ee naga iyi shukansiya ku bahdile intan ka dhige , waxa qof dhaanto maleh kuwa wadoyinka jiifo walana ku dhaamaba maskax mahayan adi ado maskax laha hadana shaqenen tada , madax yariiso jaajar afyara leedahay sasa u xanaq dhawdahay

waligee meela dadka dhertahay ma arag ina ka hooseso mooye , beena haben iyo maalin aqrine yaa kugu sirano ku dhagysto mase ada camirto , siyaasi dalkan wax fiican u qabte wa yaryahay kuwa dumiyayse waxa oogu xun kuwa manta isku dagaalayo duliyaal lisku soo aruuriyo la tartansiiya mooda

waxan la yaabe doqonimadaada markan arko adigo xaaran cunaya hadana tasbiixsanaya , waxay dhaheen xoolo xaaran ma rabno hadaa aragnana ma deyneno tuugada is nacday , dalkan waxba kumadan so kordhinine maxaa ushegta abaal inad ugashe nacalad yahey
dayuusin meel liskugu keenay dhibkod wa sidan mana is dayan mana isku daayan , doqon hada maqashe aabihis wakana meel kale ha uraadin , wax walba sheegto wa qurun ku qarsoona lee

waxa ceebta ah adi waku caado waxba kulama ahan , anaga waxi na dhibaayo adi waku faraxdaa waxasna doqonimadaada waaye shisheeye kal kaal baa tahay , wax walbo dhaca ina xaarantan ka bixeynin wa lawada ogyahay yahay waligaaya ku nooled xaranta waku duqowde

dhiloyinka xafada maso tirisa maxa nagaha kudaba dhige o kaliga nin ka ah , dayuus an damiir lahena tahay wadankaga dadkiisa raptaa ina gadato wax kale kama so dhawa , indhaha waxe kula gaduuten dad dilka dhiiga muslimka dhameese  , aduunka aragaaga unecbahay hada ilahey taqani danbe meela jogo ha iman waba kugu lablaboda

shuluq caqli leh horaa lo waaye dabal dabaal dhalaa tahay wadankaga ina dhacdis basa diyaar utahay , caata qurunle caatanima la uraysaa balaayo qurun badane , afkan huurada lehaa wax walba iiga daran boosaneer ma ag fadhiya mase dad , fudedkaga haadan ka turay qof yahow waalan maxa umdan ku daba dhigay isku darajaba ma tihiine dayuus doqonima ku darsada tahay

boosanerada ku ficantahay ina qodo caqli kale malihid lacagti cidada waka dhamyse waxbana utari mayside , shaxaad ku noola tahay ado jir ah facana inta shaqystenen reera dhisten , nacala waxu ku dhale ku yaale maxa ani bas ii aragta umada kale ma iska celisid

waligaba wax ma taraa ahed anile i taqana  afkaga danbe ila soo aad , wax walba tahy ada isku ah ani waxba iima tihin dayuus yahow tunka wayn  , ilakaha burburka ah caragarka dhameye iga leexi , afkan faruuryaha wada dilacsan tixriga gale umad hakula hadlin

qurunbadanaa tahay maxa ika daba dhigay balaayo foolxuma badane , qandho qaylo badan manta dhan maxa la cabaadeysa iisheg , waxi dhacaba adaa meshan ka masuul ah shaydaanul insi , dhaqan xuma ku dishay shaydan yahey shaydanta kala jirin o gafuurka wayn
waligaba xaaran quudata aheed daraha waween xaaran le waye , aduunka qofka ogu xun ina taha la shegay hadaba ujeda runtis  , xumaan walbo wajigaage ka muuqata nacala waxa tahay ku yaale

qoom xumo ku heshiiya tihiin dun aa leedihin ma jirto adunka xuma magac oga qadaten , wacelo laso aruuriya tihiin adinkiya hada wacelo sii dhalayo nacalada idin dhale wase , qaniis qaniis aa tahay saa isku jilcinesa laga dareema

jareer jareer dhala tahay nacala meshi laga keene ku taale  , naga tag qof yahow indhaha la' nacala kugu taale adunka lagugu kadeede ado indha la' hadana dunuubtas kusii darsate , dhusuq badanaha tahay cun nacala wecelka tahay ku taale naga har
been badane hooga tahay  balaayo kula qaabdarmaate wana wareerise , doofaro laso korsada awalba aheden dhabarka ka togto dadka , jaahilin ana so aruursade nacala folxumadin ku taalo

oohin badanidaa manta shan diifka ma iska daadine wax ku amusiyo ma wayse maxa ani bas ii hor fadhisa marka oyneso , ilmahan ya isku af bari jore manta dhan ka daba calaacalayo aqas caleyk , marada nagaha ina ka shekeso ado nin wakugu ceeb

dhaqana ka dhigate manta dhan nagaha ka hadasho , foolxuma udhimane aaqirkaga qandho maliilnima badane qofki ku arka jiro ine ku hayso ku maleya , diidiin camal u guurguurane meqa saaca so socobe balayao culees badan tahay bisinke
waligaba horay usocod ma yelanesid nacala ku dhale , qaab daranidaa adna gorme nocan u hadli jirte , madax buus buuska tahay was ma buriga lagaga tume madaxa

caloosha geedka camal ku baxde iska jaf meel walba ayda kaga horeese ceebtada mahan waxan caadada waaye wax yaro xishood malihid , doqon fulay ah marka saxib ka dhigato wa iska sidan balaayo kula fulaysanate ma dadka nala gashid iska dhicine , aabaha wase banooniga noso tuus nacala kugu taale

naag habaar qabtaa tahe hanala hadlin so sameey waxa ka dalbane baqbaqda  inta iga tagto , dhila ku dhashe afka hanala so galin eeeyga tahay cune ma ana ila tirsane meesha malin maro haben ma maresid , balaayo waji danyeer ku lahaate ma ana itaqana ama anaa afka ila so aadaysa

nin waliga dhax qayliye dhahayo adi ka hor ma arag balayo been badan maxa laga fala marka laga dhax hadlayo , lacag darteda isku badile balaayo kula qab xumaate naya ma sasa ka dacad ah xishoodka laga qaad , lacaga jirkaga ku gadane xaram xaaran lagu dara ku socota ya meel kula seexanayo nacala ku dhale

qasiisad adi camal ya wax iigu daray balaayo kula foolxuma badnaage , talefanada qanaxa dadka wato lama hadlo nocaga kalena iska daa ina isku meel fadhisano xataa ma jecli  , gaasa kugu dhacay saa balwad u cuneyse cudura kalana wakugu so skcdan wa is bahdishe

sharmuuto an waliged saladina tahay ana wax iga sheege nacala kugu taale , tumasha xamar u imaate saqajanki ku dhalay was nacala wajigaga foolxumada badan ku yaalo , waligaaba saasa nagaha ogu daba laalade sharafi waka dhimate  xishood laayey

wacel an laga wacel saneen tahay dofar yahow tuuga ah ma xoolaheyga mantana uso dhigate , noloshada wa mid been iyo baqti ku dhisan qabdaro yahey qaylada badan , nolosha lagu kadeede waliga saana iska ahaane qumaya yahey qorta dheer

qumay yahow qowsaarka ah wax mataraha ah qaabta daran iga dhamow , qumay yahow qoorta dheer qabta daran naga dhamow nacala hooyada ku yaale , xoolo laso taaga tahay manta dhan anile itaqana qof kale ma haysid

waligaaba saana u dhaqan xumeen xoolaha ku dhaamo , zina ku nooshahayadunka waku kadeed mate nacala ku dhale , qaniisyada lama tirsado wadadas iga mar balayo ku dhufsatee , waligaba laba laba aheed ana dadkaa dhige nacala kugu taale eeya iska ka dhalene qanisyalyahow
xuman dhan ade ka imaate xamar wa haleese , sharmuut sharmuut dhalaa tahay nacala wasaradaada ku taale eey yahow an laga eysanen

balaayo san bocor leh waligaba saan lee meelaha u taala kuma arag ado so jeedo wax qabsanyo , indhahan aad moodo ingadaal laga riixayo iga jeedi nacala ku dhale  , waligey wax sidaada uqalow ah ma arag waxaga dhirir wa dhaafe wa doqoonimo , labadi ku dhashe kuguma mahdin adi walguugu qasaare habarna wa kororsate

showiste adi camal waligeba wa arki jire bilaa aqlaq ba tahaymaxa ardayda ku daba dhigay macalin araga tahe , showistanima la dhiman rabtaa wax yahow alwaxa ah nacala ku dhalee , walige aadame kaa xun ma arkin aduunka intasa ku noolaye
afku saqajan ina tahay wajigaga laga darema saqajan waxid ciyaal suuq ah nacala ku dhalee , balaayo caata badan o lagu baasta leh  , qandho feero weyn oo dabaal nimo badan uf

ala yaa kaa doqonsan oo kaa dabaalsan uf wax isku fal baqtiyahey , isla wareegto waaxid gabara tahay maa xishootid maxaa meelaha ku dhige , naayaa ur badanidaa balaayo qaab daran oo foolxumo badan  , waraa saa u xuntahay ma aragtid miyaa lax dhimataa u egtahaye wax isku fal

bilaa dhaqan oo aan asluub laheyn ayaa tahay qaab daro  iyo faqriyaa isku darsate , afkiisa day oo qashinka ah ilko cagaar waaxid  ma cadeeste oo ma qubeeste ahaa tahay , wajigiisa bololka ah fiiri maba xishoonayo uf saan iska badal balo dabaalnimo badanee

ilkihiisa dhaadheer maba u jeedo af balaaar waaxid  , feerihisa baakada ah lee fiiri balaayo waji alwaxaa leh adi dhana lafo naf lahaa tahay war orod na dhaaf , indhihiisa aad moodo god quraanjo iyo farahiisa tirxiga u eg lee day

war waxaan aad moodid goronyo matageeso yaa naga qabsado war orod ha nagu dhimaninee , qofkii ugu xumaa abid ayaa tahay adi kaalinta aad ee foolxumada ayaan ku doorte , ha isku dhicin lugahan qoryaha ah kuma celiyaane

cunugan nafaqo darada heyso aad moodid inee nafta ka baxooso gacanteyda ina ku dhimataa ka baqaa  , qandho calool weyn wax cunow a dile calooshisa  calool maroodi ey u ekaate  , sankiisa tuunjiga aad moodo iyo madaxiisa kala guurka ku dhacay ayaaba wax lagu qosla ah

orod feeraha isku dhex yaacay dadka kala dhuumo yaa lagugu arkinee  hadal xumo iyo foolxuma isku darsate , dabadiisa u eg dabada dameerka lee fiiri adi dad nuuce lagaa dhigi rabe , nimoo naagis waxiid qaniis wali aabaloole ahaa tahy  jeeb bidix waaxid maba xishootid naagaha ku dhex jirtaa

qof daacuun haaya tahay dhilaa ku dhashee  war maxaa nogu sastaa ma naga hartid baqtiyahow , war hooy naftaan calayada ah ilaasho qof yahow basasha kaso ureeso  qandha  shiir badanee  , naag jirkeeda ka ganacsataa tahay xishoo oo gurigaga joog waa habarowdee  , qof cudur haayaa u egtahay wajigaga wasaq dartiis wuu madoowade

naayaa saa u xuntahay hadaa ogaaan laheyd meesha ma joogteen naa orod naga dul tag , is qoror waaxid balaayahey wariifada ah  shooweste shaqbay shiines   , naayaa butuco feero weyn darbi jiifka tahay cun

caasi walidenyahow laga quuste  darbi jiifyahow koolo cabka ah balaayo dhar wasaq badan  , nacala kugu taalo dayuusow ma ana af igula imate gacanta igula imow , wajigaga bocorka u eg usheeg waxa so wado , tuurtada shaqo kugu filan ani ha igu mashqulin nacas yahow nasaha dheer

baqbaqdaada badate shaydanka ina ka saara rabtaa , naag nin ku waalate uma xumid doqon yahey feeraha wayn , nin naag ku waashe uma xumid nacas yahow nacaska kala jirin , ilakahan badeelka u eg iga jeedi balayo ilka dhaadhere

doqomadi ku dhalaa ka kentay doqonimda eey eey dhale afkaga uraaya iga si leexi , waligaaba wax ma taraa ahed walige ado wax tare maba ku arage dayuus lee ahed meel iska jiifo dharerka daadinayo , dhilo wacela aruurisa tahay cadan iyo madowba wacela ku dhashe
balayo luga qalocan dalba waynede nocasa tahay , madaxaaga gaari qashinka u eg ani ha igu so leexin  , xaaran cuna tahay xamar dabaqyo ka dhiate xoolaha masakinta kugu maqan tuuga tahay cun

shaydaan insi aa tahay wax walba inta qasta umada ku nabta dhib badnidaa , maxaa idin kala haysto adi iyo been badan bisinka  , wax ku celiya ma wayse marka isla wareegto noqonyse nimanka ku walanese nacala shaydan ku yaale

naagaha wariifoyinka reeraha dumiya ka mid tahay iiga bax qadka naaya , waxa sheegtaba wa kugu been ha igu so lifaqin shekdada qurunka badan , adi camal wa arki jire noca balwada laha tahay waliba nooc walba sa oga dhacsan taha ujeedaba , nacaladan anagu nagu dheel dheela ma soome waye wax mataraha , dayuus waaxid masuliyadada wa gabte halkasa waxa laso fadhisane waxba qaban kara iyo wa ficanahay

dhiloyinka habenada iyo malinka wareega kamid tahay sasa u qawnow  , yahuud marka kuso dhax korte wa saan camal bilaa aqlaq waxid duli  , waligaba saana been abuur u taqane qiyaanole waynaada tahay , afkaga qurmaayo ha igula imanin wax yahow qurunka badan adiga dhana iska urayo mesha gasho waka socantahay

washiinsiyadada cun ey ey dhale afka nagala bax  , doofaar doofarkisa kala jirin   madax weyn af balaar san weyn feero baako lagu baasto foolxumo oo dhan adee kula kulante , waxaan day aad moodid qof matag heyso daacuna ku haayo caloosha becteria kagaga dhacde

wajigaan jadeecada ku dhacde fiiriya adi saan maku fiicnid cancer lee ku haayo kor nabro waaxid , balaayo gaabin badan  oo af madow oo wajiga qoriyaa leh  gacmaha cudur ma kaa haayo mise dabeelaa ka marte , indhool waaxid  sanka in lagugu dhibciyaa moodaa balaayo yaraan badan gacantena ku dhimanee aakhirka

balaayo cadaan badan sida sambab  uf waa so urte qaabkaga soo u yaaalo lee hada ogaan laheyd waa is daldali laheyd  , dhagahiisa bakeylaha lee arag balo madow badan  wax isku fal noloshaa ku dhimatee , ilkihiisa ilkaha shanbayga u eh fiiri balo ilko ku tiro badan  oo madax yar

madaxiisa aad moodid canbo gees laga dhuuqe lee day iyo indhihisa aad moodid inuu cagaarshow ku dhace  , waraa dhaqan xumidaa xaa dadka afka ugu taagee maa xishootid nacalaa la qaab xuntahee , baastar baastar dhale tahay baqtiyahow oo dawada qorigaa leh lugo baasto waaxid
